g-ashore-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-waves-coming-ashore-767x1024.jpg 767w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-waves-coming-ashore-768x1025.jpg 768w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-waves-coming-ashore-1151x1536.jpg 1151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1439px) 100vw, 1439px\" /></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t    <div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t    \n\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t            <h1 class=\"uppercase mb0\">\n\t\t\t\t            \t About Cliffside Malibu\n\t\t\t\t            </h3>\n\t\t\t\t        </div>\n\t\t\t\t    </div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"breadcrumb breadcrumb-2\"><li><a href=\"https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/\" class=\"home-link\" rel=\"home\">Home</a></li><li class=\"active\">About Cliffside Malibu</li></ol>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\n<div class=\"ebor-page-wrapper\">\n\t<a id=\"home\" class=\"in-page-link\" href=\"#\"></a>\n\t<section class=\"  light-wrapper pt64 pb64  vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid light-wrapper pt64 pb64 vc_custom_1580315170002\"><div class=\"container \"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"font-size: 17px;line-height: 2;text-align: center;font-family:Cardo;font-weight:400;font-style:italic\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >We’ve managed to create an exclusive sanctuary for individuals recovering from a drug or alcohol addiction by limiting our enrollment and offering a myriad of cutting-edge treatments. Our state-of-the-art treatment methods are also paired with the talents of acupuncturists, massage therapists, holistic medicine practitioners and a Breathworks specialist.</p><div class=\"vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_grey\" ><span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l\"><span  class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span><span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r\"><span  class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span>\n</div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"text-align: left;font-family:Raleway;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Our private and secluded Malibu housing provides expansive oceanside views and exclusive access to exciting outdoor undertakings like horseback riding, surfing and hiking.</p>\n<p>At Cliffside Malibu our focus is to offer our clients all that they will need to truly combat their addictions. The effort that we have put forth in building our private housing has given us the opportunity to offer our guests unparalleled comfort and insurmountable service and attention.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" >\n\t\t<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<p>Our selection process for our doctors, nurses, and therapists is as meticulous as the one for our personal trainers, massage therapists, chefs and residential advisors. We do this to ensure that our clients have successful <a href=\"https://discoveryaddictionservices.com/locations/cliffside-malibu/about/\">recoveries</a> that last for the rest of their lives.</p>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"image-bg overlay parallax  light-wrapper normal-padding  vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid light-wrapper normal-padding vc_custom_1580398543628\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"background-image-holder\">\n\t\t\t    <img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Background\" class=\"background-image\" src=\"https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/cliffside-malibu-beach-yoga.jpg?id=25239\" />\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"container \"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h2 style=\"color: #003057;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >GET THE HELP YOU NEED TODAY</h2>\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t    <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\"> <a class=\"btn btn-lg mb0 mt-xs-24\" href=\"/admissions\" target=\"_blank\">Take the First Step</a>\n\t\t    </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"row light-wrapper  light-wrapper pt0 pb0   light-wrapper pt0 pb0 \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc-hoverbox-wrapper  sub-header vc-hoverbox-shape--square vc-hoverbox-align--center vc-hoverbox-direction--default vc-hoverbox-width--100\"  ontouchstart=\"\">\n  <div class=\"vc-hoverbox\">\n    <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-inner\">\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-front\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/cliffside-malibu-light-blue-background-1024x512.jpg);\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-front-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 32px;color: #ffffff;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Life at Cliffside</h2>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-back\" style=\"background-color: #ebebeb;\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-back-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Life at Cliffside</h2>\n            <p>Treatment programs at Cliffside Malibu have been designed to facilitate a full recovery from addiction.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"vc_btn3-container vc_btn3-center\" ><a onmouseleave=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#003057'\" onmouseenter=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='#003057'; this.style.color='#ffffff';\" style=\"border-color:#003057; color:#003057;\" class=\"vc_general vc_btn3 vc_btn3-size-md vc_btn3-shape-square vc_btn3-style-outline-custom\" href=\"/life-at-cliffside/\" title=\"\">Learn More</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc-hoverbox-wrapper  sub-header vc-hoverbox-shape--square vc-hoverbox-align--center vc-hoverbox-direction--default vc-hoverbox-width--100\"  ontouchstart=\"\">\n  <div class=\"vc-hoverbox\">\n    <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-inner\">\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-front\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/cliffside-malibu-medium-blue-background-1024x512.jpg);\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-front-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 32px;color: #ffffff;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Life After Cliffside</h2>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-back\" style=\"background-color: #ebebeb;\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-back-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Life After Cliffside</h2>\n            <p>The goal of treatment is to create within you the skills and ability to remain clean and sober at home.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"vc_btn3-container vc_btn3-center\" ><a onmouseleave=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#003057'\" onmouseenter=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='#003057'; this.style.color='#ffffff';\" style=\"border-color:#003057; color:#003057;\" class=\"vc_general vc_btn3 vc_btn3-size-md vc_btn3-shape-square vc_btn3-style-outline-custom\" href=\"/life-after-cliffside/\" title=\"\">Learn More</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row light-wrapper  light-wrapper pt0 pb0   light-wrapper pt0 pb0 \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc-hoverbox-wrapper  sub-header vc-hoverbox-shape--square vc-hoverbox-align--center vc-hoverbox-direction--default vc-hoverbox-width--100\"  ontouchstart=\"\">\n  <div class=\"vc-hoverbox\">\n    <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-inner\">\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-front\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/cliffside-malibu-medium-blue-background-1024x512.jpg);\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-front-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 32px;color: #ffffff;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Why Cliffside?</h2>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-back\" style=\"background-color: #ebebeb;\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-back-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >Why Cliffside?</h2>\n            <p>The answer is simple. We want you to go to treatment once and recover for good.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"vc_btn3-container vc_btn3-center\" ><a onmouseleave=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#003057'\" onmouseenter=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='#003057'; this.style.color='#ffffff';\" style=\"border-color:#003057; color:#003057;\" class=\"vc_general vc_btn3 vc_btn3-size-md vc_btn3-shape-square vc_btn3-style-outline-custom\" href=\"/why-choose-cliffside/\" title=\"\">Learn More</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc-hoverbox-wrapper  sub-header vc-hoverbox-shape--square vc-hoverbox-align--center vc-hoverbox-direction--default vc-hoverbox-width--100\"  ontouchstart=\"\">\n  <div class=\"vc-hoverbox\">\n    <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-inner\">\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-front\" style=\"background-image: url(https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/cliffside-malibu-light-blue-background-1024x512.jpg);\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-front-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 32px;color: #ffffff;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >View Our Facility</h2>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block vc-hoverbox-back\" style=\"background-color: #ebebeb;\">\n        <div class=\"vc-hoverbox-block-inner vc-hoverbox-back-inner\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;text-align: center;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >View Our Facility</h2>\n            <p>Cliffside Malibu is a beautiful luxury estate, situated on two acres, overlooking Zuma Beach.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"vc_btn3-container vc_btn3-center\" ><a onmouseleave=\"this.style.borderColor='#003057'; this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#003057'\" onmouseenter=\"this.style.bor