      "rawText": "About Cliffside Malibu - Reimagine Recovery at Our Luxurious Program \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n CALL FOR A CONFIDENTIAL CONSULTATION \n Call \n 424.320.3061 \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n Treatment Programs \n \n \n Levels of Care \n \n \n Detox \n\n \n Residential Treatment Program \n\n \n\n \n The Stages of Change \n\n \n Treatment Modalities \n \n \n Somatic Experiencing and EMDR \n\n \n Dialectical Behavior Therapy \n\n \n Cognitive Behavioral Therapy \n\n \n Motivational Interviewing \n\n \n Family Systems Therapy \n\n \n\n \n Experiential &#038; Holistic Therapy \n \n \n Acupuncture \n\n \n Massage \n\n \n Mindsight &#038; Interpersonal Neurobiology \n\n \n Relapse Prevention Therapy \n\n \n Yoga Therapy \n\n \n\n \n Treatment Directory \n\n \n\n Your Experience \n \n \n Why Choose Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n Life at Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n Life After Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n\n About \n \n \n Our Approach \n\n \n Our Team \n\n \n Locations \n\n \n Tour \n\n \n Brochure \n\n \n What We Treat \n\n \n Blog \n\n \n State Licensing \n\n \n\n Insurance \n\n Contact \n \n \n Admissions \n\n \n\n Careers \n\n \n\n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n About Cliffside Malibu\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n Home \n\nAbout Cliffside Malibu\n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n\nWe’ve managed to create an exclusive sanctuary for individuals recovering from a drug or alcohol addiction by limiting our enrollment and offering a myriad of cutting-edge treatments. Our state-of-the-art treatment methods are also paired with the talents of acupuncturists, massage therapists, holistic medicine practitioners and a Breathworks specialist.\n\n \n\nOur private and secluded Malibu housing provides expansive oceanside views and exclusive access to exciting outdoor undertakings like horseback riding, surfing and hiking.\n\nAt Cliffside Malibu our focus is to offer our clients all that they will need to truly combat their addictions. The effort that we have put forth in building our private housing has given us the opportunity to offer our guests unparalleled comfort and insurmountable service and attention.\n\n \n\n \n\n \nOur selection process for our doctors, nurses, and therapists is as meticulous as the one for our personal trainers, massage therapists, chefs and residential advisors. We do this to ensure that our clients have successful recoveries that last for the rest of their lives.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\nGET THE HELP YOU NEED TODAY\n\n \n\n \n Take the First Step \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nLife at Cliffside\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nLife at Cliffside\n\n \nTreatment programs at Cliffside Malibu have been designed to facilitate a full recovery from addiction.\n\n \n Learn More \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nLife After Cliffside\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nLife After Cliffside\n\n \nThe goal of treatment is to create within you the skills and ability to remain clean and sober at home.\n\n \n Learn More \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nWhy Cliffside?\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nWhy Cliffside?\n\n \nThe answer is simple. We want you to go to treatment once and recover for good.\n\n \n Learn More \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nView Our Facility\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nView Our Facility\n\n \nCliffside Malibu is a beautiful luxury estate, situated on two acres, overlooking Zuma Beach.\n\n \n Learn More \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nTHE BEST CALL YOU WILL EVER MAKE\n\nCall now to speak confidentially with an admission counselor.\n\n (424) 320-3061 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n 0/5 \n \n (0 Reviews) \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n Drug and Alcohol Treatment Center \nAdmissions Office (424) 320-3061 24hrs\n\nFollow Us\n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\nCompany Information\n \n \n About Us \n\n Careers \n\n News Press \n\n Contact Us \n\n Patient Portal \n\n \n\nSelect Language\n \n\nUseful Information\n \n \n FAQs \n\n Insurance \n\n Treatment Programs \n\n Locations \n\n \n\nSearch\n \n \n \n\nHighest Treatment Standard\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n Licensed by the  State Department of Health Care Services \n\nIf this is a life-threatening emergency, please call 911 or the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at (800) 273-8255 \n\n© 2025 Cliffside Malibu | Website branding by Evertype Brand Design \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n Top \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n Cliffside Malibu has a fresh look and experience. Visit our new website today.",
