ge-title-3 image-bg overlay\"><div class=\"background-image-holder\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore.jpg\" class=\"background-image\" alt=\"Cliffside Malibu - Gentle Waves Coming Ashore\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore.jpg 1280w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/cliffside-malibu-gentle-waves-coming-ashore-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t    <div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t    \n\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t            <h1 class=\"uppercase mb0\">\n\t\t\t\t            \t Admissions\n\t\t\t\t            </h3>\n\t\t\t\t        </div>\n\t\t\t\t    </div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"breadcrumb breadcrumb-2\"><li><a href=\"https://www.cliffsidemalibu.com/\" class=\"home-link\" rel=\"home\">Home</a></li><li class=\"active\">Admissions</li></ol>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\n<div class=\"ebor-page-wrapper\">\n\t<a id=\"home\" class=\"in-page-link\" href=\"#\"></a>\n\t<section class=\"  light-wrapper pt64 pb64  vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid light-wrapper pt64 pb64 \"><div class=\"container \"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"font-size: 17px;line-height: 2;text-align: center;font-family:Cardo;font-weight:400;font-style:italic\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >At Cliffside Malibu, we offer two comprehensive programs – primary treatment and extended care – to assist our clients in achieving lasting sobriety. Each of our new clients participates in a medical and mental health screening by our staff physician, a clinical therapist and a psychiatrist. These screenings help you and your therapist design a unique treatment plan that reflects the needs identified during this evaluation process. A treatment plan identifies specific challenges you and your therapist believe should be addressed during your stay at Cliffside, while it also provides a tool for measuring progress.</p><div class=\"vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_grey\" ><span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l\"><span  class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span><span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r\"><span  class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span>\n</div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_column-gap-20\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 18px;color: #003057;text-align: left;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >PRIMARY TREATMENT ADMISSION GUIDELINES</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;font-family:Raleway;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >We welcome individuals who satisfy the following requirements:</p>\n\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" >\n\t\t<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>You are over 18 years of age</li>\n<li>You are chemically dependent upon drugs/alcohol</li>\n<li>You are able to perform a reasonable level of self-care, including, eating, grooming and maintaining orderliness in your living quarters</li>\n<li>You express motivation and a willingness to live in a treatment environment and pursue a sober life.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 18px;color: #003057;text-align: left;font-family:Tenor Sans;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >EXTENDED CARE ADMISSION GUIDELINES</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;font-family:Raleway;font-weight:400;font-style:normal\" class=\"vc_custom_heading\" >We welcome individuals who satisfy the following requirements:</p>\n\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" >\n\t\t<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>You are over 18 years of age</li>\n<li>You are currently sober – no longer chemically dependent on drugs/alcohol.</li>\n<li>You are willing to follow a treatment plan developed by you and your therapist.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><a id=\"contact\" class=\"in-page-link\" href=\"#\"></a><section class=\"  light-wrapper normal-padding  vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid light-wrapper normal-padding \"><div class=\"container \"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t<div class=\"wpb_raw_code wpb_content_element wpb_raw_html\" >\n\t\t<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<h4 style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #93988c; line-height: 1; text-align: center; font-family: Tenor Sans; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal;\">THE BEST CALL YOU WILL EVER MAKE</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px;\">Call now to speak confidentially with an admission counselor.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"cta-phone-number\" href=\"tel:+14243203061\" style=\"text-align: center !important;\">(424) 320-3061</a><br><br>\r\n\t\r\n\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></section>\n</div>\n\n<footer class=\"footer-1 bg-dark\">\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n    \n        <div class=\"row\">\n  