      "rawText": "Cliffside Malibu Admission Process and Assessment \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n CALL FOR A CONFIDENTIAL CONSULTATION \n Call \n 424.320.3061 \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n Treatment Programs \n \n \n Levels of Care \n \n \n Detox \n\n \n Residential Treatment Program \n\n \n\n \n The Stages of Change \n\n \n Treatment Modalities \n \n \n Somatic Experiencing and EMDR \n\n \n Dialectical Behavior Therapy \n\n \n Cognitive Behavioral Therapy \n\n \n Motivational Interviewing \n\n \n Family Systems Therapy \n\n \n\n \n Experiential &#038; Holistic Therapy \n \n \n Acupuncture \n\n \n Massage \n\n \n Mindsight &#038; Interpersonal Neurobiology \n\n \n Relapse Prevention Therapy \n\n \n Yoga Therapy \n\n \n\n \n Treatment Directory \n\n \n\n Your Experience \n \n \n Why Choose Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n Life at Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n Life After Cliffside Malibu \n\n \n\n About \n \n \n Our Approach \n\n \n Our Team \n\n \n Locations \n\n \n Tour \n\n \n Brochure \n\n \n What We Treat \n\n \n Blog \n\n \n State Licensing \n\n \n\n Insurance \n\n Contact \n \n \n Admissions \n\n \n\n Careers \n\n \n\n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n Admissions\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n Home \n\nAdmissions\n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n\nAt Cliffside Malibu, we offer two comprehensive programs – primary treatment and extended care – to assist our clients in achieving lasting sobriety. Each of our new clients participates in a medical and mental health screening by our staff physician, a clinical therapist and a psychiatrist. These screenings help you and your therapist design a unique treatment plan that reflects the needs identified during this evaluation process. A treatment plan identifies specific challenges you and your therapist believe should be addressed during your stay at Cliffside, while it also provides a tool for measuring progress.\n\n \n\nPRIMARY TREATMENT ADMISSION GUIDELINES\n\nWe welcome individuals who satisfy the following requirements:\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nYou are over 18 years of age\n\nYou are chemically dependent upon drugs/alcohol\n\nYou are able to perform a reasonable level of self-care, including, eating, grooming and maintaining orderliness in your living quarters\n\nYou express motivation and a willingness to live in a treatment environment and pursue a sober life.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEXTENDED CARE ADMISSION GUIDELINES\n\nWe welcome individuals who satisfy the following requirements:\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nYou are over 18 years of age\n\nYou are currently sober – no longer chemically dependent on drugs/alcohol.\n\nYou are willing to follow a treatment plan developed by you and your therapist.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \nTHE BEST CALL YOU WILL EVER MAKE\n\nCall now to speak confidentially with an admission counselor.\n\n (424) 320-3061 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n Drug and Alcohol Treatment Center \nAdmissions Office (424) 320-3061 24hrs\n\nFollow Us\n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n\nCompany Information\n \n \n About Us \n\n Careers \n\n News Press \n\n Contact Us \n\n Patient Portal \n\n \n\nSelect Language\n \n\nUseful Information\n \n \n FAQs \n\n Insurance \n\n Treatment Programs \n\n Locations \n\n \n\nSearch\n \n \n \n\nHighest Treatment Standard\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n Licensed by the  State Department of Health Care Services \n\nIf this is a life-threatening emergency, please call 911 or the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at (800) 273-8255 \n\n© 2025 Cliffside Malibu | Website branding by Evertype Brand Design \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n \n\n Top \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n\n \n\n \n Cliffside Malibu has a fresh look and experience. Visit our new website today.",
